{"tid":2294744,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇有啲區議員助理成日諷刺啲街坊咩都搵佢地幫","createTime":"2020-11-21T09:02:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T08:02:09.000Z","uid":46161,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"59a7ca6197eae896893cd1ac62721c291752a96c","tid":2294744,"uid":46161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T09:02:34.000Z","msg":"派飯比啲低收入，有黃絲低收入者撐侵侵，就比佢地串：拎飯啦！有飯食先講政治。<br />\n<br />\n街坊搵佢地幫手搞漏水嘅野，又比佢串： 都唔知點解要花時間做依啲野。<br />\n<br />\n派消毒野比街坊，有街坊拎唔到，好聲好氣去問佢地有冇，又比佢串： 我地唔係做派野架，你拎唔到你自己搞掂啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人地話有投比佢地，轉個頭係fb： 投票比我地大撚晒咩！<br />\n<br />\n依啲助理真係.....唔想做唔好做啦..."},{"pid":"49918b3ffc7b1f3cd23c5169812ae36f0e560ad0","tid":2294744,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T09:03:19.000Z","msg":"講事實者"},{"pid":"d41a394910ad27249b53df8126ffc1939d06867d","tid":2294744,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T09:04:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"957c8908c0a82c36b34450fca456732606819292","tid":2294744,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T09:04:31.000Z","msg":"咁有啲人真係好似議員助理係奴隸咁"},{"pid":"390f861f1832e1b692d5caa707c6dcc5c3ca587f","tid":2294744,"uid":206594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T09:05:16.000Z","msg":"開名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b74316a7bb769da86af6b175c6e198b61583d05","tid":2294744,"uid":244460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T09:05:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bde80509eec282e48588c9cd6e3d58a5ff91c73a","tid":2294744,"uid":76068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T09:06:06.000Z","msg":"我果邊區議員連工業噪音都唔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d508a3ea8ff6c6d1abf7c73aeb2d6c1f45ef35c5","tid":2294744,"uid":46161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T08:02:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal